	new API as needed.

2004-10-30 17:57  castaglia

	* contrib/mod_ifsession.c: 
	There is not enough information to call resolve_deferred_dirs() at
	session init time.  This function is usually for expanding the
	tilde in path names, and at session init time, we don't know the
	user name for expansion.

