	Update the release notes with mention of TimeoutLinger.

2004-05-21 10:19  castaglia

	* NEWS, include/data.h, modules/mod_core.c, src/data.c: 
	Add a TimeoutLinger option.  It's just simpler to change this value
	via the config file, for those sites that encounter troubles with
	lingering closes, rather than requiring a reconfigure and
	recompile.

