	* NEWS, modules/mod_ls.c: 
	Bug#2367 - LIST *.* strange behaviour.

2004-03-22 11:44  castaglia

	* doc/howto/: Authentication.html, Chroot.html, ConfigFile.html,
	Debugging.html, Directory.html, Limit.html, TLS.html, Vhost.html: 
