	* contrib/mod_tls.c: 
	Didn't mean to commit those debugging changes.	Oops.

2004-03-03 17:33  castaglia

	* contrib/mod_tls.c: 
	No need to be that verbose.

2004-03-03 13:21  castaglia

	* contrib/mod_tls.c: 
	Handle the case where mod_tls has been configured to set
	environment variables but the client does not present a certificate
	(e.g. when not verifying clients).  Previously, this would cause a
	segfault.

