	* contrib/mod_sql.c: 
	Note the directive name when warning of deprecated * usage.

2004-02-15 14:05  castaglia

	* contrib/mod_sql.c: 
	Disable the "*" functionality in SQLAuthenticate, which was used to
	configure mod_sql to be authoritative.	This conflicts with the
	AuthOrder configuration directive, which should be used instead.

