	* config.h.in, configure.in, include/conf.h: 
	Configure detection/use for <netinet/in_systm.h> header; this fixes
	compile errors on BSD platforms.  Patch contributed by Daniel
	Svensson.

2003-06-16 13:22  castaglia

	* NEWS, src/dirtree.c, src/sets.c: 
	Bug#2088: proftpd -t segfault.	The functional change of this patch
	is using parent_pool, rather than c_pool, in start_sub_config()
	when allocating a new xaset *.	The rest of the patch is style
	cleanup.

