	Solaris 2.6 or 2.7 box, we'll use struct statvfs, otherwise,
	statvfs_t.  We'll deal with those poor souls still using 2.5.1 or
	older later.  (Thanks for the info about statvfs64 on Solaris 2.7,
	Noah).

