	siblings.

2003-04-14 23:42  castaglia

	* NEWS, src/main.c: 
	Bug#2021 - Inetd mode and scoreboard format changes.  Now, if
	ServerType is inetd and the server encounters a scoreboard version
	mismatch on startup, the old scoreboard file will be unlinked and a
	new blank one written.

